Name:         Tardigrade
Scientific:   Ramazzottius varieornatus
Class:        Tardigrada
Habitat:      Everywhere
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     2.5 years
Weight:       1e-07 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Nearly indestructible; survives space vacuum, radiation, extreme temps

Name:         Emperor Penguin
Scientific:   Aptenodytes forsteri
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Antarctic
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     25 years
Weight:       45 kg
Status:       Near Threatened
Fact:         Deepest-diving bird at 565m; male incubates egg 65 days without eating

Name:         Arctic Fox
Scientific:   Vulpes lagopus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Arctic tundra
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     3 years
Weight:       3.5 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Fur changes color seasonally; survives -70 degrees Celsius

